examples.en: Suddenly he jerked back in his chair.
The sound of the phone jerked me awake.
In spite of his fear, he jerked out his request.
She jerked open the car door and got out.
He turned the handle and jerked the door open.
Doyle jerked at the girl's hair, to make her sit down.
The sound of her voice jerked my mind back to the present.
Wilcox jerked his head to indicate that they should move on.
He jerked his head round and saw something that chilled his blood.
The mouth was slightly open, and jerked violently and spasmodically at one corner.
